    "body": "A workaround is to just add `bool public IS_SCRIPT = true;` to the `CommonDeployer` â€” this isn't used anywhere else afaik so it shouldn't cause any issues.\r\n\r\nAnother thing you could do is just merge `PolygonDeployer` and `CommonDeployer` into a single contract so it is a script, and then in your test you do `MyTest is Test, PolygonDeployer` and call `PolygonDeployer.run()` in setup, and the broadcasts basically just act like pranks",
